        Children's Story Hour</h4>
    <p>
        Please join us for Saturday Morning Story Hour at RPC! Each Saturday we feature a beautiful picture book, a fun craft, a snack, and a game. Parents are welcome to stay and enjoy refreshments during story hour. 
        </p>
    <br />
    <div>
<b>Time</b>: 9 AM to 10 AM<br />
<b>Date</b>: Every Saturday, unless falling on a major holiday.<br />
<b>Ages</b>: 3-10 (older children are welcome if they wish to attend, younger children accompanied by a parent are also welcome!)<br />
<b>Cost</b>: Free<br />
<b>Registration</b>: Sign in when you arrive!</div>
